{"tid":2062641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚惠珠：中國能立於不敗之地！","createTime":"2020-06-13T09:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T12:17:33.000Z","uid":7542,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e65606576a379d7d7bdf51675da9eb088f5e75c2","tid":2062641,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">有冇人數吓中國敗咗幾多次</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》委員會副主任譚惠珠在香港電台節目《香港家書》表示，回歸後的香港，對中國而言，是一個長期重用的特別行政區，中央一定不會弄垮香港。她又表示，在香港訂立國安法，中央其實等了23年，直到香港有人表明一定擋住第23條立法，中央就不得不出手。以下為譚惠珠的書信全文：<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n訂立港區國安法事在必行，在短期內亦會有爭議，但今日的中國，在國際社會上，無論是在經濟、環保、衛生醫療合作，聯合國的維和工作等，<strong><ins>都處處顯示了她是個有能力、承擔的國家，能立於不敗之地</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n國家對香港的支持將不會變。<strong><ins>疫情期間，我們沒有缺水、缺糧，或者日用必須品。</ins></strong>日前，為了保持香港作為航空樞紐，香港政府一舉用200多人億元挽救一間英資為最大股東的航空公司。有人會提出，那是香港土地基金的錢，其實香港的土地是屬國家所有，但收入歸香港，香港亦從來沒有向國家繳稅，<strong><ins>我們還懷疑中央對香港的好意嗎</ins></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/譚惠珠：中央一定不會弄垮香港/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%BC%84%E5%9E%AE%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=0f396f3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.master-insight.com/譚惠珠：中央一定不會弄垮香港/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DWcWvLk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWcWvLk.jpg&h=396b3265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">^補返張J圖先</span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中國未必乜都贏<br />\n但係中共一定鬥乜都贏</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong> <span style=\"color: orange;\">連幫你填中國國歌歌詞嗰個都可以批鬥死</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong> <br />\n</span> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q74yKaeTqB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ74yKaeTqB0&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=41725949\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q74yKaeTqB0</a>"},{"pid":"5d4a036be7df7fe6fa7595ef6c0e448823b895a2","tid":2062641,"uid":39010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:30:18.000Z","msg":"一日共慘黨係到<br />\n死鳩晒平民都不敗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e8e56be5ea309644ee6ff8c8c5417ff3188ef2","tid":2062641,"uid":173179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"人無恥便無敵嘛"},{"pid":"be06a7eef06d0a3f33346aae6eb039e5e997b4ec","tid":2062641,"uid":201751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"點解連豬咁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻人形豬咁on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd71f9858e4446a39c47a60606f69592c0cb50e6","tid":2062641,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"贏贏贏贏贏贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a141873b86a5d68976a12db5a0a7460fcc595246","tid":2062641,"uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:34:44.000Z","msg":"我更加唔明白香港沒有缺水、缺糧，或者日用必須品，關深圳河隔離嗰個國家咩事... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cafe3b95d54d61f9851659d5f73785631135807","tid":2062641,"uid":192776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"支那或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s